# LOCAL DEVELOPMENT (default) — values below are the Supabase CLI's
# well-known local defaults. They are NOT secret; every local Supabase CLI
# install on every machine uses the same ones unless you change
# supabase/config.toml. Safe to commit as defaults, but copy this file to
# .env.local (gitignored) rather than editing this file directly.
#
# To get these confirmed/refreshed for your machine, run:
#   supabase start
# then `supabase status` to print them again at any time.

