# PRODUCTION / SERVER DEPLOYMENT — when you deploy this app to a real server,
# you'll run a separate Supabase stack there too (self-hosted via Docker, see
# README "Deploy to a server"). Replace the three values above with that
# server's own URL and freshly generated keys — never reuse the local dev
